<h3>

Below you will find the quiz I created for my Napier University 
Web Technology class. The reason I chose a geography related quiz is 
because this subject is something that I am passionate about. 
I have been lucky enough to travel to many places throughout the 
world and seen many of the landmarks on this quiz. 
I hope you all enjoy and wish you all the best of luck!

</h3>

